<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

    <title>Whiskiki | 위스키 등록 요청하기</title>
    <link href="https://unpkg.com/material-components-web@latest/dist/material-components-web.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/material-components-web@latest/dist/material-components-web.min.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons">
    <style>
      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      body {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100vh;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      h1 {
        margin-top: 40px;
        margin-bottom: 40px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 22px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #222;
      }

      li {
        display: flex;
        margin-top: 20px;
        align-items: center;
        list-style: none;
      }
      img {
        margin-right: 10px;
      }

      h2 {
        margin-top: 40px;
        color: #222;
        font-size: 20px;
        font-weight: 700;
      }

      form {
        padding: 0 26px;
      }

      p {
        margin-top: 12px;
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #7d7d7d;
      }
      
      .field {
        margin-top: 20px;
      }
      .filebox {
        display: flex;
      }
      label {
        width: 100%;
      }
.filebox .upload-name {
    display: inline-block;
    height: 40px;
    padding: 0 10px;
    vertical-align: middle;
    border: 1px solid #dddddd;
    width: 78%;
    color: #999999;
}
.filebox label {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0px 20px;
    color: #fff;
    vertical-align: middle;
    background-color: #999999;
    cursor: pointer;
    line-height: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    margin-left: 10px;
    max-width: 60px;
}
.filebox input[type="file"] {
    position: absolute;
    width: 0;
    height: 0;
    padding: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 0;
}
.center {
  position: absolute;
  left: 0;
  bottom: 60px;
  width: 100%;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
}
.submit-button {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  width: 150px;
  height: 52px;
  color: white;
  background-color: #F39D37;
  border-radius: 8px;
  border: none;
  font-size: 18px;
}
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>위스키 등록 요청하기</h1>
    <form method="post" action="/v1/api/whisky/request" enctype="multipart/form-data">
      <div class="field">
        <label class="mdc-text-field mdc-text-field--filled name">
          <span class="mdc-text-field__ripple"></span>
          <span class="mdc-floating-label" id="my-label-id">이름</span>
          <input class="mdc-text-field__input" type="text" name="name" required aria-labelledby="my-label-id">
          <span class="mdc-line-ripple"></span>
        </label>
      </div>

      <div class="field">
        <label class="mdc-text-field mdc-text-field--filled category">
          <span class="mdc-text-field__ripple"></span>
          <span class="mdc-floating-label" id="my-label-id">종류</span>
          <input class="mdc-text-field__input" type="text" name="category" aria-labelledby="my-label-id">
          <span class="mdc-line-ripple"></span>
        </label>
      </div>

      <div class="field">
        <label class="mdc-text-field mdc-text-field--filled country">
          <span class="mdc-text-field__ripple"></span>
          <span class="mdc-floating-label" id="my-label-id">국가</span>
          <input class="mdc-text-field__input" type="text" name="country" aria-labelledby="my-label-id">
          <span class="mdc-line-ripple"></span>
        </label>
      </div>

      <h2>관련된 위스키 사진이 있다면 첨부해주세요.</h2>
      <p>첨부 파일 등록은 최대 1개까지 가능합니다.</p>

      <div class="field">
        <div class="filebox">
          <input class="upload-name" value="첨부파일" placeholder="첨부파일">
          <label for="file">파일찾기</label> 
          <input id="file" type="file" name="photo" />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="field center">
        <button type="submit" class="submit-button">
          제출하기
          <span class="material-icons">
file_download
</span>
        </button>
      </div>
    </form>

    <script>
      new mdc.textField.MDCTextField(document.querySelector('.field .name'));
      new mdc.textField.MDCTextField(document.querySelector('.field .category'));
      new mdc.textField.MDCTextField(document.querySelector('.field .country'));

      document.querySelector('#file').addEventListener('change',function(){
        const fileName = document.querySelector('#file').value;
        document.querySelector('.upload-name').value = fileName.split('\\').pop();
      });
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
